{"tid":2182702,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日晚 吉寸 串燒","createTime":"2020-08-31T13:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T11:18:56.000Z","uid":310853,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"69684b27b8023fbf969bedb56dad753121e35192","tid":2182702,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dspJmxr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdspJmxr.png&h=2bd614c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見咁多人講就去下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/80B0oL4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F80B0oL4.png&h=5a2a9b71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n燒原塊豬頸肉湯烏冬 - $54<br />\n$50 左右主食都係合理價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n豬頸肉的確算幾多 合乎返佢個價格<br />\n咬落去係淋身 唔似出面好多舖頭咁係非常硬<br />\n而且有爽口感 食到有少少咸味 <br />\n我唔知佢本身係醃過定燒時有上汁<br />\n豬頸肉係真係幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n湯底就應該似壽喜燒昆布湯嗰類 少甜<br />\n烏冬份量唔係太多 類似日式嗰類份量<br />\n如果主食想飽d就可能要揀返飯類<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FQhfcGW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFQhfcGW.png&h=0cbb839a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9dJ2B8G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9dJ2B8G.png&h=65456415&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個波我冇嗌到 佢送嘅 唔知咩嚟<br />\n<br />\n燒生蠔 - $42 x2<br />\n太耐冇食串燒嘢 價錢應該算合理掛<br />\n生蠔唔係超大隻嗰款<br />\n但蒜蓉落得足 而且加上跟返個外殼比例睇<br />\n都燒得幾好 冇乜點縮水<br />\n落到舖頭見到原來蟶子都差唔多價錢<br />\n蟶子應該會再正d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n燒羊架 - $33<br />\nD味我就幾鍾意 正常發揮<br />\n但價錢方面我諗下次應該會轉食其他嘢<br />\n今次真係太求其嗌 冇細心睇<br />\n見佢有牛舌芯 同 白鱔<br />\n同其他特別小小嘅嘢<br />\n牛舌芯就好大興趣<br />\n如果有食過牛舌<br />\n佢一塊有紅色同粉紅色嘅位<br />\n而粉紅色就最矜貴最好食<br />\n唔知佢個牛舌芯會唔會就係依回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n整體嚟講都相當唔錯<br />\n依間應該再過多一段時間會夾fd去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c54b546e6d1626bff334e1323bebdcb1366c426","tid":2182702,"uid":123848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:02:12.000Z","msg":"無竹簽叫得串燒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b352d9a23f6128485028a69534e6ef0a9bf5268f","tid":2182702,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:02:22.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n好食<br />\n我都食過"},{"pid":"7f18c381bb30bfc1d720e580ada3eb3ff06a3da3","tid":2182702,"uid":284922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:02:28.000Z","msg":"生蠔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db274d04b3dc7c49b51d6b7987bb1d8527b9747a","tid":2182702,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:02:38.000Z","msg":"睇落好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e9668065a3bda660b0b5c0f5d938d0782ce65d","tid":2182702,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c54b546e6d1626bff334e1323bebdcb1366c426","tid":2182702,"uid":123848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:02:12.000Z","msg":"無竹簽叫得串燒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:03:11.000Z","msg":"佢其他有 咁啱我揀嗰d冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db67f7613c0ff1cc960d5a610aa220d3c2ada5fc","tid":2182702,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b352d9a23f6128485028a69534e6ef0a9bf5268f","tid":2182702,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:02:22.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n好食<br />\n我都食過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:05:35.000Z","msg"